                     <interp inst="t18190421-246-person2289" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I am clerk to Mr. Bull, who is a silversmith, and lives in Cheapside. I bought two spoons of a boy about the age of the prisoner, for 4 s. 9 d. I did not ask him any questions.</p>

